; ============================================================
; INVENTORY 2 of 2 — PROVIDER INVENTORY (VirtualBox)
; ad/Scenario3/providers/virtualbox/inventory
; Contains actual management IPs (192.168.57.x) from Vagrantfile.
; Edit this file when IPs change.
; ============================================================
; Per-host ansible_ssh_private_key_file rather than a templated
; [all:vars] value — {{ inventory_hostname }} in [all:vars] was
; resolving empty for some Ansible/inventory-merge configurations.

